《'''国歌'''》（{{lang-tg|Суруди Миллӣ}}）是[[塔吉克斯坦|塔吉克斯坦]]的[[国歌|国歌]]，1991年采用。由古尔纳扎·凯尔地作词，苏莱曼·亚达科夫作曲。曲调原为[[塔吉克苏维埃社会主义共和国国歌|苏联时期塔吉克斯坦的国歌]]，1994年重新填词，曲调沿用至今。<ref>Tiago José Berg. ''Hinos de todos os países do mundo''. Panda Books, 2008. p. 262. ISBN 9788578882358.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.com.br/books?id=I4AZDMbwU7oC&pg=PA709&dq=7+september+1994+tajikistan+anthem&hl=pt-BR&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjNqPynm9DMAhUMkZAKHc2bCnQQ6AEIJjAA#v=onepage&q=7%20september%201994%20tajikistan%20anthem&f=false |title=Tadzhikistan Legal Texts:The Foundations of Civic Accord and a Market Economy |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2020-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609030157/https://books.google.com.br/books?id=I4AZDMbwU7oC&pg=PA709&dq=7+september+1994+tajikistan+anthem&hl=pt-BR&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjNqPynm9DMAhUMkZAKHc2bCnQQ6AEIJjAA#v=onepage&q=7%20september%201994%20tajikistan%20anthem&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="si">{{Cite web |url=http://si-dushanbe.tj/en/nationam-anthem/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-06-09 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027042930/http://si-dushanbe.tj/en/nationam-anthem/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

